This is Director Brassel.
Ethan Hunt is attempting
to escape the building.

1005
01:17:16,293 --> 01:17:18,128
He's in the west
cargo elevator.
He must be stopped.

1006
01:17:18,128 --> 01:17:21,081
I want Mendoza and Graham
in the situation room
right away.

1007
01:17:21,081 --> 01:17:23,049
I'm having the building
surrounded, sir.

