01:17:28,054 --> 01:17:30,340
It's Hunt.
I know it's Hunt.

1012
01:17:32,392 --> 01:17:34,895
Hunt was flagged
on sub-basement nine.

1013
01:17:34,895 --> 01:17:38,732
