1148
01:30:56,862 --> 01:31:00,232
You gotta get us out of here.
I lost the signal.

1149
01:31:02,902 --> 01:31:04,787
You okay?
Not yet.

1150
01:31:13,129 --> 01:31:13,913
(DIALLING)
Come on. Come on.

1151
01:31:21,804 --> 01:31:23,306
I don't have a signal.
I don't have a signal.

1152
01:31:23,306 --> 01:31:24,390
I'm on it. I'm on it.
I'm on it!

1153
01:31:31,597 --> 01:31:33,065
(GRUNTS)

1154
01:31:33,065 --> 01:31:34,150
Zhen!

1155
